      {
        "role": "user",
        "content": "我没有注意到刚才你在全量编译我以为卡了，所以我关掉了现在你继续，而且编译你可以聪明一点，不用编译的你可以别编译"
      },
      {
        "role": "assistant",
        "content": "刚才并不是正常的全量编译卡住：`key_down/key_pressed` 少链接了 `libvmstack.a`，随后批处理仍遍历 500 多个历史 DLL 做哈希，最后被关闭。现在改成增量路径，只重建 `vmstate` 和 8 个新增 mod，并直接用 Python 计算/重命名这 8 个文件，不再扫描历史 DLL。另外热跳转必须清空旧调用帧，否则多次插入/删除后会留下失效返回地址。我会把这个语义放在 VM 的通用 `cvm_replace_current` 中，然后执行增量编译；这是运行时控制流修复，不会重新引入编辑器整合状态。",
        "tool_calls": [
          {
            "id": "call_3SqhzrrTJAMMLSr0tOOGh8T8",
            "type": "function",
            "function": {
              "name": "python",
              "arguments": "{\"code\":\"from pathlib import Path\\nimport subprocess, os, hashlib\\nroot=Path(r'C:\\\\Users\\\\12159\\\\Desktop\\\\Singularity')\\np=root/'vmstate.c'; s=p.read_text()\\nold='''__declspec(dllexport) void cvm_replace_current(const H k, u8 *base) {\\n    if (k) memcpy(cur_key, k, 32);\\n    cur_base = base;\\n    ptr = base;\\n}'''\\nnew='''__declspec(dllexport) void cvm_replace_current(const H k, u8 *base) {\\n    frame_sp = 0;\\n    if (k) memcpy(cur_key, k, 32);\\n    cur_base = base;\\n    ptr = base;\\n}'''\\nif s.count(old)!=1: raise RuntimeError('replace-current anchor mismatch')\\np.write_text(s.replace(old,new),encoding='ascii',newline='\\\\n')\\nprint('updated vmstate frame reset')\\nenv=os.environ.copy(); env['PATH']=r'C:\\\\mingw64\\\\bin;'+env.get('PATH','')\\ncommands=[\\n ['cmd','/c','build_vmstate.bat'],\\n ['gcc','-shared','mods_src/key_down.c','-o','mods/key_down.dll','libcont.a','libvmstack.a','libvmstate.a','-luser32'],\\n ['gcc','-shared','mods_src/key_pressed.c','-o','mods/key_pressed.dll','libcont.a','libvmstack.a','libvmstate.a','-luser32'],\\n ['gcc','-shared','mods_src/block_select_payload.c','-o','mods/block_select_payload.dll','libcont.a','libvmstate.a','libvmstore.a','libvm.a','-lws2_32','-ladvapi32'],\\n ['gcc','-shared','mods_src/block_offset_at_index.c','-o','mods/block_offset_at_index.dll','libcont.a','libvmstack.a','libvmstate.a','libvmstore.a'],\\n ['gcc','-shared','mods_src/block_token_hex.c','-o','mods/block_token_hex.dll','libcont.a','libvmstack.a','libvmstate.a','libvmstore.a'],\\n ['gcc','-shared','mods_src/u32_hex.c','-o','mods/u32_hex.dll','libcont.a','libvmstack.a'],\\n ['gcc','-shared','mods_src/drawtext_stack.c','-o','mods/drawtext_stack.dll','libcont.a','libvmstack.a','libvmstate.a','libdxgfx.a'],\\n ['gcc','-shared','mods_src/jump_payload.c','-o','mods/jump_payload.dll','libvmexec.a','libvmstate.a','libvmstore.a','libvm.a','-lws2_32','-ladvapi32'],\\n]\\nfor cmd in commands:\\n r=subprocess.run(cmd,cwd=root,env=env,text=True,encoding='utf-8',errors='replace',capture_output=True,timeout=30)\\n print('OK' if r.returncode==0 else 'FAIL', ' '.join(cmd))\\n if r.stdout.strip(): print(r.stdout[-1000:])\\n if r.stderr.strip(): print(r.stderr[-2000:])\\n if r.returncode: raise SystemExit(r.returncode)\\nprint('hash rename')\\nfor name in ['key_down','key_pressed','block_select_payload','block_offset_at_index','block_token_hex','u32_hex','drawtext_stack','jump_payload']:\\n p=root/'mods'/f'{name}.dll'; h=hashlib.sha256(p.read_bytes()).hexdigest(); dst=p.with_name(h+'.dll')\\n if not dst.exists(): p.replace(dst)\\n else: p.unlink()\\n print(name,h,dst.stat().st_size)\"}"
            }
          }
        ]
